      "author": "Ongiei",
      "description": "## 0.3.8\\n\\n- Download ECDICT directly from skywind3000/ECDICT instead of a LexiBridge-hosted data package.\\n- Add selectable GitHub, ghproxy.net, gh-proxy.com, jsDelivr, Fastly, GCore, and Statically nodes with a speed-test action.\\n- Show ECDICT installation progress in a persistent Obsidian Notice instead of a modal.\\n- Reorganize settings into local dictionary, word notes, reading and links, Youdao enhancement, Eudic sync, and advanced sections.\\n- Stop writing LexiBridge managed-block comments into notes. Preserve user content under one or more configurable Markdown headings.\\n- Create synchronized notes through a temporary non-Markdown file and rename after Obsidian settles, avoiding Templater's new-Markdown template path and reducing Flexplorer event races.\\n- Remove the obsolete ECDICT packaging tool and runtime compression dependency.",
